            <h1>Our Mission</h1>
            <p>Welcome to City Sprouts Collective! We are a collective of passionate gardeners, designers, and foodies dedicated to exploring urban sustainability in Southeast Asia.</p>
            <p>Our story began in 2022 with a simple idea: what if we brought together different voices—the botanist, the designer, the home cook, the community organizer—to share a more holistic view of green living in our cities? The world of urban farming is vast and ever-changing, and we believe that the best ideas come from collaboration.</p>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to build a vibrant community around urban farming and sustainable living. We aim to provide you with insightful, high-quality content that inspires, educates, and sparks conversation. From growing your own food to reducing waste in the kitchen, we cover it all.</p>
            <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
            <p>City Sprouts Collective is powered by a team of dedicated writers and creators. We are horticulturists, sustainable design advocates, home cooks, and community organizers who bring our unique experiences to the table. You can get to know each of us and read our contributions on our Team Page.</p>
            <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
            <p>We believe that you, our reader, are part of our team. We encourage you to join the conversation by commenting on our posts and following our projects on Instagram and in our private Facebook Group.</p>
            <p>Ready to dive in? Explore our latest articles on growing, cooking, and sustainable living.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Include the footer partial -->
